INITIATIVES        Peer Mentoring  Peer mentor program to help transition new students into college and the CS field.       Team Projects  Work with peers to develop a programming project and beef up your resume!       Professional Development  Join us for professional workshop or get involved with LOGICA leadership.       Community Outreach  Volunteer to build the UIC CS community or to help local middle school students explore computer science.       Company Talks and Workshops  Come listen to industry members talk about their job, their field, and possible internship or job opportunities.       Panels  Come to our tech talks to learn about what is happening in the field of computer science with leaders in academia and industry.            Get Involved           Calendar
